calling it a reign of terror he urged church leaders to seek 
support for pressure on the beijing government to put an end to 
all persecution and ensure those who have already been arrested are 
given fair trials 
the letter also discussed another sensitive issue in hong kong 
the wave of vietnamese who have sailed from their communist homeland 
