was part of a bullet 
root remained in stable condition under heavy sedation at 
hollywoods memorial hospital today 
his odyssey started on a flight from washington to rocky mount 
nc and ended when he crashed after his singleengine plane ran 
out of fuel 10000 feet above bahamian waters early thursday 
afternoon 
