instruct us representatives at international financial 
institutions to oppose all loans to china 
review the advisability of continuing to extend to china 
mostfavorednation trade treatment 
review all trade agreements between the two countries 
review commercial agreements governing chineseamerican 
cooperation on satellite launches 
review the chineseamerican agreement on the peaceful uses of 
atomic energy 
