probably would ask the legislature to consider abortion restrictions 
if another special session is held later this year in florida gov 
bob martinez said he would call a special session of the legislature 
in october to consider abortion bills 
clearly i believe the unborn ought to have more rights than 
they have right now martinez said i dont believe we ought to 
wait until 1990 to deal with a difficult subject its not something 
thats going to go away 
